The FCC ID for this device covers both the [[TRENDnet TEW-713RE]] and the [[TRENDnet TEW-714TRU]].
This particular unit also has a USB charging-only port (as well as one standard USB 2.0 port).
"7018N-A107-03" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
Default SSID, OUI, and login credentials are per a marketplace (eBay) label.
